OL,3,C'Shock' in community after death of
OL,4,Cwoman in Derry
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a young
OL,7,Fmother whose death is at the centre of
OL,8,Fa murder investigation in Londonderry.
OL,10,FThe mum of two, named locally as Amy
OL,11,FDoherty, aged in her 20s, died in
OL,12,Fhospital on Saturday.
OL,14,FPolice are continuing to question a 30-
OL,15,Fyear-old man who has been arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,18,FLocal representatives told UTV the
OL,19,Fcommunity has been left "shocked and
OL,20,Fsaddened".
OL,26,@{D@YOU
