OL,3,C'Shock' in community after death of
OL,4,Cwoman in Derry
OL,6,FSinn Fein MLA Ciara Ferguson said:
OL,7,F"Amy was such a beautiful, kind,
OL,8,Floving girl and she will be missed so
OL,9,Fsorely by everyone, obviously her
OL,10,Fimmediate family, but likewise across
OL,11,Fthe community, her friends as well."
OL,13,FDUP Alderman Niree McMorris said: "I
OL,14,Fjust beggars belief that somebody's
OL,15,Fhome is where they should feel safe
OL,16,Fand unfortunately for this girl it was
OL,17,Fthe end of her life."
OL,26,@nD@Grr
