PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774278664
OL,3,C'Shock' in community after death of
OL,4,Cwoman in Derry
OL,6,FSDLP MLA Mark H Durkan said: "People
OL,7,Faround here are absolutely shocked,
OL,8,Fthis is a quiet area, and people are
OL,9,Fjust reeling at the fact that this has
OL,10,Fhappened."
OL,12,FPolice were called to a property in
OL,13,Fthe Summer Meadows Mews area of Derry
OL,14,Fon Saturday morning and a woman was
OL,15,Ftaken to hospital where she later died.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
