OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774278664
OL,3,C'Shock' in community after death of
OL,4,Cwoman in Derry
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "Detectives from
OL,7,Fthe Police Service of Northern
OL,8,FIreland's Major Investigation Team
OL,9,Fhave launched a murder investigation
OL,10,Ffollowing the death of a woman in
OL,11,FDerry/Londonderry on Saturday, 21st
OL,12,FMarch.
OL,14,F"Officers attended a property in the
OL,15,FSummer Meadows Mews area of the city
OL,16,Fat around 10.20 am and located an
OL,17,Finjured woman at the scene.
OL,19,F"She was taken to hospital by our
OL,20,Fcolleagues in the NIAS where she sadly
OL,21,Fdied.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@AOU
