PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774278664
OL,3,C'Shock' in community after death of
OL,4,Cwoman in Derry
OL,6,F"A 30-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of murder.
OL,9,F"Our thoughts are with her family and
OL,10,Floved ones, who are left trying to
OL,11,Fcome to terms with this shocking loss.
OL,13,F"Our enquiries are continuing, and I
OL,14,Fam appealing to anyone with
OL,15,Finformation, no matter how
OL,16,Finsignificant it may seem, to contact
OL,17,Four officers on 101."
